                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280703-134-off674 t18280703-134-crimeloc677"></join>. On the 21st of June, I saw the prisoner go into the shop and come out with the cheese under his arm - he rather ran than walked; he dropped the cheese - I took it up, and he was taken.</p>
               <p>Cross-examined by MR. ADOLPHUS. Q. Did you take notice of his features or dress? A. No, but he was in my sight, from the time he went into the shop till he was taken - this is the cheese.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280703-134-person823">
